  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Reference Medicinal Products (RMPs) from 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">There will be changes to the legislation of Reference Medicinal Products (RMPs) used to support abridged marketing authorisation applications from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

